query:
WITH ranked_objects AS (
        SELECT sid, scraper, 
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY sid
            ORDER BY time_stamp DESC
        ) AS rn 
        FROM scraper_touched_sitzung
        )
        DELETE FROM scraper_touched_sitzung st
        USING ranked_objects ro
        WHERE st.sid=ro.sid AND
        st.scraper=ro.scraper AND
        ro.rn > $1
